mplementation to ensure it aligns with our plan and follows best practices\" <commentary>A numbered step from the planning document has been completed, so the code-reviewer agent should review the work.</commentary></example>\n","model":"inherit"},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"key":"00_System/Links/Gemini_Extensions/superpowers/agents/code-reviewer.md"},
